  "instructions": [
    "Heat the amaranth seed oil in a pan over medium heat.",
    "Add the quinoa and wild rice, cooking for 2 minutes, stirring occasionally.",
    "Add the grass-fed butter, stirring until melted.",
    "Add the dried cranberries, coconut milk, and chopped chives, stirring to combine.",
    "Bring the mixture to a simmer, then reduce heat to low and cook for 20 minutes, stirring occasionally.",
    "Season with sea salt to taste.",
    "Serve hot in an earthenware bowl.",
    "Garnish with additional chopped chives if desired.",
    "Let the pilaf rest for 5 minutes before serving."
